'''辛偉誠'''（{{Lang-en|Rishi Sunak}}，{{Bd|1980年|5月12日}}）是[[英国|英国]][[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]政治家，自2020年2月13日起因應[[2020年英國內閣改組|內閣改組]]接替[[薩吉德·賈偉德|薩吉德·賈偉德]]出任[[財政大臣_(英國)|財政大臣]]。辛偉誠於[[2015年英國大選|2015年英國大選]]中在[[英国下议院|下議院]][[里奇蒙_(約克郡)_(英國國會選區)|列治文（約克郡）國會選區]]當選，成為國會議員，並在2019年7月24日起為時任財政大臣薩吉德·賈偉德的[[財政部首席秘書|財政部首席秘書]]，直至自己出任財政大臣。

辛偉誠出生於英國[[漢普郡|漢普郡]][[南安普敦|南安普敦]]的一個[[旁遮普人|旁遮普裔]]家庭。辛偉誠曾在[[温切斯特公学|温切斯特公学]]就讀，然後在[[牛津大学|牛津大学]][[牛津大学林肯学院|林肯学院]]修讀[[哲學、政治學及經濟學|哲學、政治學及經濟學]]，後來在[[斯坦福商学研究生院|斯坦福商学研究生院]]以[[福布莱特计划|福布莱特学友]]的身份後獲得[[工商管理碩士|工商管理碩士]]（{{Lang|en|MBA}}）學位。畢業後，辛偉誠在[[高盛|高盛]][[投资银行|投资银行]]工作，後來成為[[对冲基金|对冲基金]]管理公司[[TCI|TCI]]的合作夥伴。

== 早年生活 ==
辛偉誠在1980年5月12日出生於英國漢普郡南安普敦<ref name=":0"/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Who is the new chancellor Rishi Sunak?|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-51490893|accessdate=2020-02-13|author=Espiner|date=2020-02-13|first=Tom|publisher=BBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213142047/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-51490893|archivedate=2020-02-13}}</ref>，是雅殊韋爾·薩納克（{{Lang|en|Yashvir Sunak}}）與烏沙·薩納克（{{Lang|en|Usha Sunak}}）之子<ref name=Gunn/>。辛偉誠的祖父母都出生在[[印度|印度]][[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]]，並在1960年代由[[东非|东非]]移民到英國<ref name="Business2"/>。他的父親雅殊韋爾是一名[[一般科醫師|一般科醫師]]，而他的母親烏沙則是在當地營運藥房的[[藥劑師|藥劑師]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Sunak, Rt Hon. Rishi (born 12 May 1980)|url=https://www.ukwhoswho.com/view/10.1093/ww/9780199540884.001.0001/ww-9780199540884-e-283888|accessdate=2019-10-01|publisher=A & C Black|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213151328/https://www.ukwhoswho.com/view/10.1093/ww/9780199540884.001.0001/ww-9780199540884-e-283888|archivedate=2020-02-13}}</ref><ref name="Gunn">{{Cite book|first=Simon|last=Gunn|first2=Rachel|last2=Bell|title=Middle Classes: Their Rise and Sprawl|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=s98O6mjm94UC&pg=PT109|date=2011-06-16|publisher=Orion|isbn=978-1-78022-073-4|page=109|access-date=2020-03-17|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125539/https://books.google.com/books?id=s98O6mjm94UC&pg=PT109&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.easterneye.biz/lists/rishi-sunak/|work=Eastern Eye|accessdate=2019-10-01|title=Rishi Sunak|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125540/https://www.easterneye.biz/lists/rishi-sunak/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。辛偉誠是家中的長子，而他的家中共有三兄弟姐妹<ref name=Business2/>。

辛偉誠在寄宿男校温切斯特公学就讀，並是該校的{{le|學生代表|Head girl and head boy}}<ref name="Telegraph"/>。他其後在牛津大學林肯學院修讀哲學、政治學及經濟學，並於2001年<ref name=":0"/>以第一名畢業<ref name=Telegraph/>。2006年，他以福布莱特学友的身份獲得斯坦福商学研究生院的工商管理碩士學位<ref name=":0"/><ref name="econindia"/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Narayana Murthy's son-in-law Rishi Sunak enters British parliament with a thumping victory|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/Narayana-Murthys-son-in-law-Rishi-Sunak-enters-British-parliament-with-a-thumping-victory/articleshow/47206790.cms|accessdate=2015-05-09|author=Kounteya Sinha|date=2015-05-09|work=The Times of India|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928050926/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/Narayana-Murthys-son-in-law-Rishi-Sunak-enters-British-parliament-with-a-thumping-victory/articleshow/47206790.cms|archivedate=2016-09-28}}</ref>。

== 從商 ==
從2001年到2004年，辛偉誠在高盛投資銀行擔任分析師<ref name=":0"/><ref name="Business">{{Cite news|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/quite-positive-that-rishi-will-do-well-as-a-mp-says-murthy-115050800943_1.html|work=Business Standard|date=2015-05-08|accessdate=2019-10-01|title=Quite positive that Rishi will do well as a MP, says Murthy|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102233041/http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/quite-positive-that-rishi-will-do-well-as-a-mp-says-murthy-115050800943_1.html|archivedate=2016-01-02}}</ref>。他其後在對沖基金管理公司TCI任職，並在2006年9月成為公司的合作夥伴<ref>{{Cite web|title=TCI adds four partners|url=https://www.fnlondon.com/articles/tci-adds-four-partners-20070124|accessdate=2019-10-01|author=Hutchings|date=2007-01-24|first=William|publisher=Financial News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725051540/https://www.fnlondon.com/articles/tci-adds-four-partners-20070124|archivedate=2019-07-25}}</ref>。他在2009年離開TCI<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rishi Sunak|url=https://register.fca.org.uk/ShPo_IndividualDetailsPage?id=003b000000LVKnuAAH|accessdate=2019-10-01|publisher=Financial Conduct Authority|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125539/https://register.fca.org.uk/s/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並加入了他的舊同事在2010年10月以7億美元開立的新對沖基金公司佛廉基金（{{Lang|en|Theleme Partners}}）<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ft.com/content/37c77240-50e8-11e1-8cdb-00144feabdc0|title=Ex-TCI star emerges at rival|work=Financial Times|date=2012-02-07|accessdate=2019-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190921065205/https://www.ft.com/content/37c77240-50e8-11e1-8cdb-00144feabdc0|archivedate=2019-09-21}}{{Subscription required}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ft.com/content/75c1e2da-dfb3-11df-bed9-00144feabdc0|title=Star analyst's new fund raises $700m|work=Financial Times|date=2010-10-25|accessdate=2019-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725053502/https://www.ft.com/content/75c1e2da-dfb3-11df-bed9-00144feabdc0|archivedate=2019-07-25}}{{Subscription required}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Tomorrow's Titans|url=https://thehedgefundjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/THFJ-Tomorrows-Titans-survey.pdf|accessdate=2019-10-01|publisher=The Hedge Fund Journal|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125539/https://thehedgefundjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/THFJ-Tomorrows-Titans-survey.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。辛偉誠也曾在他的印度裔商人岳父{{le|那格哇·勒馬堯·那拉揚·穆菲|N. R. Narayana Murthy}}開立的投資公司長筏風險投資（{{Lang|en|Catamaran Ventures}}）任職<ref name=Business/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Narayana Murthy far behind Azim Premji in family office stakes|url=https://www.livemint.com/companies/news/narayana-murthy-far-behind-azim-premji-in-family-office-stakes-1549917473062.html|accessdate=2019-10-01|author=Sood|date=2019-02-12|first=Varun|publisher=Livemint|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125540/https://www.livemint.com/companies/news/narayana-murthy-far-behind-azim-premji-in-family-office-stakes-1549917473062.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 從政 ==
=== 國會議員 ===
2014年10月，辛偉誠被選定為列治文（約克郡）國會選區的保守黨候選人。該選區先前由前[[保守黨領袖_(英國)|保守黨黨魁]]及前[[外交及聯邦事務大臣|外交大臣]][[夏偉林|夏偉林]]出任議員，惟夏偉林選擇不再在下一次大選中競選連任<ref name="Telegraph"/>。同年，他成為{{le|政策交流委員會|Policy Exchange}}智庫黑人及少數族裔研究組的領導，並參與了一份有關英國黑人及少數族裔的報告的合寫<ref name="PE"/>。他在2015年的大選當選為列治文（約克郡）國會選區議員，並取得了19,550票多數票（得票率36.2%）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Richmond (Yorks)|url=https://electionresults.parliament.uk/election/2015-05-07/results/Location/Constituency/Richmond%20(Yorks)|accessdate=2019-10-01|publisher=parliament.uk|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125543/https://electionresults.parliament.uk/election/2015-05-07/results/Location/Constituency/Richmond%20%28Yorks%29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在{{le|2015年英國大選當選議員列表|List of MPs elected in the 2015 United Kingdom general election|該屆國會}}中參與了{{le|英國下議院環境、食品和鄉村事務委員會|Environment, Food and Rural Affairs Select Committee|環境、食品和鄉村事務委員會}}<ref name="parlbio"/>。

辛偉誠在2016年6月舉行的[[英國去留歐盟公投|英國去留歐盟公投]]中支持英國退出[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]（脫歐）<ref>{{Cite web|title=EU vote: Where the cabinet and other MPs stand|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-eu-referendum-35616946|accessdate=2019-10-01|date=2016-06-22|publisher=BBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003020914/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-eu-referendum-35616946|archivedate=2017-10-03}}</ref>。同年，他為[[撒切尔主义|撒切尔主义]]智庫{{le|政策研究中心|Centre for Policy Studies}}撰寫了一份支持在英國脫歐後設立[[自由港|自由港]]的報告。翌年，他撰寫了一份支持為[[中小型企業|中小型企業]]設立零售債券市場的報告<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-focus-fears-grow-over-new-chancellors-taxlite-free-ports-push-a4366221.html|work=Evening Standard|title=Business focus: Fears grow over new Chancellor's tax-lite free ports push|date=2020-02-19|accessdate=2020-02-20|author=Armitage|first=Jim|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125557/https://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-focus-fears-grow-over-new-chancellors-taxlite-free-ports-push-a4366221.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=A New Era for Retail Bonds|url=https://www.cps.org.uk/files/reports/original/171116092827-ANewEraforRetailBonds.pdf|accessdate=2020-02-20|author=Sunak|date=November 2017|first=Rishi|publisher=Centre for Policy Studies|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125602/https://www.cps.org.uk/files/reports/original/171116092827-ANewEraforRetailBonds.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/news/opinion/columnists/rishi-sunak-a-better-budget-way-for-smes-to-access-cash-for-growth-1-8868258|work=Yorkshire Post|title=Rishi Sunak: A better Budget way for SMEs to access cash for growth|author=Sunak|first=Rishi|date=2017-11-21|accessdate=2020-02-20|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220162750/https://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/news/opinion/columnists/rishi-sunak-a-better-budget-way-for-smes-to-access-cash-for-growth-1-8868258|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

辛偉誠在[[2017年英國大選|2017年的大選]]當選連任，並獲得23,108票多數票（得票率40.5%），比上次大選取得更多的多數票<ref>{{Cite web|title=Richmond (Yorks)|url=https://electionresults.parliament.uk/election/2017-06-08/results/Location/Constituency/Richmond%20(Yorks)|accessdate=2019-10-01|publisher=parliament.uk|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190113041036/http://electionresults.parliament.uk/election/2017-06-08/results/Location/Constituency/Richmond%20(Yorks)|archivedate=2019-01-13}}</ref>。他自2018年1月9日起至2019年7月24日出任地方政府事務{{le|副國務大臣|Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State}}<ref name="parlbio">{{Cite web|title=Rt Hon Rishi Sunak MP|url=https://www.parliament.uk/biographies/commons/rishi-sunak/4483|accessdate=2019-10-01|publisher=parliament.uk|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731113418/https://www.parliament.uk/biographies/commons/rishi-sunak/4483|archivedate=2019-07-31}}</ref>。他投票贊成時任[[英国首相|英国首相]][[文翠珊|文翠珊]]的脱歐協議，並投票反對[[英国二次脱欧公投请愿|進行第二次脫歐公投]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://ig.ft.com/brexit-exit-deal-vote/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902092554/https://ig.ft.com/brexit-exit-deal-vote/|archivedate=2019-09-02|date=2019-03-29|title=How MPs voted on May's withdrawal deal defeat|work=Financial Times}}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。他在[[2019年英国保守党领袖选举|2019年的保守黨黨魁選舉]]中支持[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]成為黨魁，並和他的國會議員朋友[[羅伯特·詹里克|羅伯特·詹里克]]和[[奧利佛·道登|奧利佛·道登]]在約翰遜於當年6月競選期間在《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》共同撰文支持約翰遜<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/the-tories-are-in-deep-peril-only-boris-johnson-can-save-us-3xq9lrvr3|work=The Times|date=2019-06-05|author=Sunak|first=Rishi|author2=Jenrick|first2=Robert|last3=Dowden|first3=Oliver|title=The Tories are in deep peril. Only Boris Johnson can save us|accessdate=2020-02-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200103100034/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/the-tories-are-in-deep-peril-only-boris-johnson-can-save-us-3xq9lrvr3|archivedate=2020-01-03}}{{Subscription required}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/moderates-back-boris-johnson-to-be-next-prime-minister-vk2n72psm|work=The Times|date=2019-06-05|title=Moderates back Boris Johnson to be next prime minister|author=Zeffmann|first=Henry|author2=Elliott|first2=Francis|accessdate=2020-02-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709210809/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/moderates-back-boris-johnson-to-be-next-prime-minister-vk2n72psm|archivedate=2019-07-09}}{{Subscription required}}</ref>。

辛偉誠在[[2019年英國大選|2019年的大選]]再度當選連任，並獲得27,210票多數票（得票率47.2%），比上次大選取得更多的多數票<ref>{{Cite web|title=Richmond (Yorks)|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14000895|accessdate=2019-12-13|publisher=BBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726183856/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14000895|archivedate=2019-07-26}}</ref>。他在競選期間代表保守黨出席[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]和[[獨立電視台_(英國)|獨立電視台]]舉辦的7次選舉辯論<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2019/nov/29/election-debate-the-nights-winners-and-losers|work=The Guardian|title=Election debate: the night's winners and losers|accessdate=2019-12-14|date=2019-11-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209044741/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2019/nov/29/election-debate-the-nights-winners-and-losers|archivedate=2019-12-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2019/dec/01/sturgeon-in-control-to-better-opponents-in-itv-debate|work=The Guardian|title=ITV election debate: the winners and the losers|accessdate=2019-12-14|date=2019-12-01|author=Mason|first=Rowena|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209043945/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2019/dec/01/sturgeon-in-control-to-better-opponents-in-itv-debate|archivedate=2019-12-09}}</ref>。

=== 財政部 ===
2019年7月24日，英國首相約翰遜任命辛偉誠為財政部首席秘書<ref>{{Cite web|title=Full list of new ministerial and government appointments: July 2019|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/full-list-of-new-ministerial-and-government-appointments-july-2019|accessdate=2019-10-01|date=2019-07-30|publisher=gov.uk|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804043111/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/full-list-of-new-ministerial-and-government-appointments-july-2019|archivedate=2019-08-04}}</ref>。辛偉誠在翌日隨即成為[[英國樞密院|英國樞密院]]的成員之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Orders Approved and Business Transacted at the Privy Council Held by the Queen at Buckingham Palace on 25th July 2019|url=http://privycouncil.independent.gov.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019-07-25-List-of-Business.pdf|accessdate=2019-07-30|date=2019|publisher=Privy Council Office|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730112009/http://privycouncil.independent.gov.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019-07-25-List-of-Business.pdf|archivedate=2019-07-30}}</ref>。2020年2月13日，薩吉德·賈偉德因為被約翰遜要求辭退所有特別顧問而辭職。辛偉誠在同日隨即因應内閣改組升任財政大臣<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cabinet reshuffle: Sajid Javid resigns as chancellor|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-51491662|accessdate=2020-02-13|date=2020-02-13|publisher=BBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213120158/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-51491662|archivedate=2020-02-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/feb/13/sajid-javid-resigns-as-chancellor-amid-boris-johnson-reshuffle|work=The Guardian|title=Sajid Javid resigns as chancellor amid Johnson reshuffle|date=2020-02-13|accessdate=2020-02-13|author=Mason|first=Rowena|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213121054/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/feb/13/sajid-javid-resigns-as-chancellor-amid-boris-johnson-reshuffle|archivedate=2020-02-13}}</ref>。

2020年3月11日，辛偉誠宣讀他的{{le|2020年3月英國政府財政預算案|March 2020 United Kingdom budget|首份財政預算案}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Budget 2020 to remain on 11 March, new Chancellor Rishi Sunak confirms|url=https://news.sky.com/story/budget-to-remain-on-11-march-new-chancellor-rishi-sunak-confirms-11937001|accessdate=2020-02-18|author=Heffer|date=2020-02-18|first=Greg|publisher=Sky News|archive-date=2022-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110160322/https://news.sky.com/story/budget-to-remain-on-11-march-new-chancellor-rishi-sunak-confirms-11937001|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該財政預算案包括300億英鎊的額外開支，其中120億英鎊用於減輕[[2019冠状病毒病英国疫情|COVID-19大流行]]對英國帶來的經濟影響<ref>{{cite news|title=Budget 2020: Chancellor pumps billions into economy to combat coronavirus|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-51835306|accessdate=2020-03-11|date=2020-03-11|publisher=BBC News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200311142741/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-51835306|archive-date=2020-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月17日不到一周的時間裡，辛偉誠公佈了包括由政府提供的3,300億英鎊企業貸款及延長商業稅減免措施等應對大流行的緊急措施<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-51935467|title=Coronavirus: Chancellor unveils £350bn lifeline for economy|date=2020-03-17|accessdate=2020-03-18|publisher=BBC News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317174307/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-51935467|archive-date=2020-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月20日，辛偉誠公佈了給予無法工作且列入於其雇主的工資單的雇員其工資的80%（最高2,500英鎊）的措施，是英國政府首次推出如此的員工保留計劃<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-51982005|title=Coronavirus: Government to pay up to 80% of workers' wages|publisher=BBC News|date=2020-03-20|accessdate=2020-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320171928/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-51982005|archive-date=2020-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2020/mar/20/government-pay-wages-jobs-coronavirus-rishi-sunak|work=The Guardian|title=UK government to pay 80% of wages for those not working in coronavirus crisis|date=2020-03-20|accessdate=2020-03-20|last=Partington|first=Richard|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320180824/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2020/mar/20/government-pay-wages-jobs-coronavirus-rishi-sunak|archive-date=2020-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
辛偉誠在2009年8月娶[[印孚瑟斯|印孚瑟斯]]共同創始人之一[[那格哇·勒馬堯·那拉揚·穆菲|那格哇·勒馬堯·那拉揚·穆菲]]的女兒[[阿克沙塔·穆菲|阿克沙塔·穆菲]]（{{lang|en|Akshata Murthy}}，1980年4月-）<ref>[https://www.politics.co.uk/reference/akshata-murthy-profile/ 《Murthy, Akshata》：“（Akshata）Murthy was born in April 1980 in Hubli, a small town 250 miles north of Bangalore.”]</ref>為妻子。他們二人在[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]首次相遇，現在有兩個女兒<ref name="Telegraph">{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/world/murthy-son-in-law-gets-hagues-seat/cid/1586703|work=The Telegraph|date=2014-10-20|accessdate=2019-10-01|title=Murthy son-in-law gets Hague's seat|author=Roy|first=Amit|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125619/https://www.telegraphindia.com/world/murthy-son-in-law-gets-hagues-seat/cid/1586703|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="econindia">{{Cite web|title=Sudha-Narayana Murthy's son-in-law Rishi Sunak wins polls as Conservative party member|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/nri/nris-in-news/sudha-narayana-murthys-son-in-law-rishi-sunak-wins-polls-as-conservative-party-member/articleshow/47209420.cms|accessdate=2015-05-09|date=2015-05-09|work=The Economic Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150512011704/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/nri/nris-in-news/sudha-narayana-murthys-son-in-law-rishi-sunak-wins-polls-as-conservative-party-member/articleshow/47209420.cms|archivedate=2015-05-12}}</ref>。辛偉誠是[[印度教|印度教]]的{{le|印度教徒|Hindus|教徒}}<ref name="Business2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/opinion/lunch-with-bs-rishi-sunak-115080601060_1.html|title=UK Cabinet member Rishi Sunak on being British, Indian & Hindu at same time|work=Business Standard|author=Puri|first=Anjali|date=2015-08-10|accessdate=2019-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726105820/https://www.business-standard.com/article/opinion/lunch-with-bs-rishi-sunak-115080601060_1.html|archivedate=2019-07-26}}</ref>，而他自2017年起在英國下議院以《[[薄伽梵譚|薄伽梵譚]]》進行宣誓<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/columns/democracies-can-be-strengthened-by-equal-representation-in-parliament/story-hvt8P6KiFaf6Q2JQJ5CHQL.html|work=Hindustan Times|author=Hundal|first=Sunny|date=2017-06-23|accessdate=2020-01-14|title=Democracies can be strengthened by equal representation in Parliament|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114010314/https://www.hindustantimes.com/columns/democracies-can-be-strengthened-by-equal-representation-in-parliament/story-hvt8P6KiFaf6Q2JQJ5CHQL.html|archivedate=2020-01-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/indians-abroad/alok-sharma-rishi-sunak-take-oath-on-bhagwad-gita-in-uk-s-house-of-commons/story-hNqAVICJawgjQMYg4QnffN.html|accessdate=2020-01-13|title=Indian-origin lawmakers Alok Sharma, Rishi Sunak take oath on Bhagwad Gita in UK's House of Commons|author=Sonwalkar|first=Prasun|work=Hindustan Times|date=2019-12-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112152212/https://www.hindustantimes.com/indians-abroad/alok-sharma-rishi-sunak-take-oath-on-bhagwad-gita-in-uk-s-house-of-commons/story-hNqAVICJawgjQMYg4QnffN.html|archivedate=2020-01-12}}</ref>。辛偉誠曾為{{le|東倫敦科學學校|East London Science School}}的學校董事<ref name="PE">{{Cite web|title=A Portrait of Modern Britain|url=https://policyexchange.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/a-portrait-of-modern-britain.pdf|accessdate=2020-02-20|publisher=Policy Exchange|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213210952/https://policyexchange.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/a-portrait-of-modern-britain.pdf|archivedate=2020-02-13}}</ref>。

== 軼聞 ==
辛偉誠在擔任財政大臣並宣讀他的首份財政預算案後，成為了英國媒體追逐的對象。[[天空新闻台|天空新闻台]]主播{{le|莊拿芬·森姆斯|Jonathan Samuels}}表示，製作團隊在製作節目時為了配合旁白中提到的「綠色預算」（{{lang|en|Green budget}}），刻意把他走出官邸的片段中他手上的紅色文件夾的顏色在鏡頭前變成綠色。此舉成功在世界各地引起話題，其中更有部分網民一度將畫面聯繫到攝影機的濾鏡的效果與[[藍黑白金裙|藍黑白金裙]]事件。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.taisounds.com/w/TaiSounds/society_20031313355307831|title=資料夾在鏡頭前從紅色變綠色，巫術般的神秘現象讓網友腦洞大開|website=太報|date=2020-03-13|accessdate=2020-03-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319025346/https://www.taisounds.com/w/TaiSounds/society_20031313355307831|archivedate=2020-03-19|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

